ic league only***''</small>\n\n===[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Top goalscorers]]===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"  style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; \"\n! style=\"background:#ff0000; color:white;\" scope=\"col\"|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|#]]\n! style=\"background:#ff0000; color:white;\" scope=\"col\"|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Name]]\n! style=\"background:#ff0000; color:white;\" scope=\"col\"|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Years]]\n! style=\"background:#ff0000; color:white;\" scope=\"col\"|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Goals]]\n|-\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|1]]|| align=\"left\" |{{flagicon|NGA}} Bartholomew Ogbeche\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|2018-19]]||[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{sort|12|'''12''' (18)}}]]\n|-\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|2]]|| align=\"left\" |{{flagicon|ARG}} Nicol\u00e1s V\u00e9lez\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|2015-2016]]||[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{sort|8|'''8''' (25)}}]]\n|-\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|3]]|| align=\"left\" |{{flagicon|ARG}} Emiliano Alfaro\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|2016]]||[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{sort|5|'''5''' (13)}}]]\n|-\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|4]]|| align=\"left\" |{{flagicon|IND}} Seiminlen Doungel\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|2014-2018]]||[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{sort|5|'''5''' (25)}}]]\n|-\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|5]]|| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|URY}} Federico Gallego\n|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|2018-]]||[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{sort|5|'''5''' (28)}}]]\n|-\n|[[List of NorthEas