EN}}]][[Venezuela]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|30 June 2015]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|20 December 2015]]\n|-\n|scope=row style=text-align:left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Nelo Vingada]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{POR}}]][[Portugal]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|23 July 2016]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|15 May 2017]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Vingada leaves NorthEast United FC|url=https://twitter.com/NEUtdFC/status/864024738435260416|website=NorthEast United FC (Twitter)}}</ref>\n|-\n|scope=row style=text-align:left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Jo\u00e3o de Deus]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{POR}}]][[Portugal]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|17 July 2017]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|3 January 2018]]\n|-\n|scope=row style=text-align:left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Avram Grant]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{ISR}}]][[Israel]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|4 January 2018 <br /> <small>(caretaker)</small> <br /> 12 January 2018 <br /><small>(Head Coach)</small>]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|14 August 2018]]\n|-\n|scope=row style=text-align:left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|Eelco Schattorie]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|{{NED}}]][[Netherlands]]\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and statistics|17 August 2018]]<ref>{{cite web|URL=https://twitter.com/NEUtdFC/status/1030446418966638593?s=19|title=Eelco appointed as Head coach|accessdate=17 August 2018}}</ref>\n|align=left|[[List of NorthEast United FC records and 